      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网场景设计一个蓝图差异与合并的状态机。核心是用L++来处理ActuatorController的配置版本对比。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
