      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以初始状态是idle，然后通过LOAD_LEFT事件进入加载左版本的状态？我命名为left_loaded可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "left_loaded",
        "LOAD_LEFT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。left_loaded之后需要加载右版本，用LOAD_RIGHT进入ready状态。ready是核心工作态，支持重复加载基准或左右版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "left_loaded",
        "ready",
        "LOAD_RIGHT",
        "LOAD_BASE",
        "LOAD_LEFT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ready的自循环我加上了。那差异分析怎么触发？需要区分单个对比和全量对比吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ready",
