      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DIFF事件进入diffing状态，完成后到diff_complete。但DIFF_ALL可以直接从ready跳到diff_complete，跳过中间态。MQTT Broker参与DIFF，EdgeNode参与DIFF_ALL。",
